data.description:
Come see this cute house in Salado in a convenient area!  This home is located close to the downtown breweries, wineries and festivals as well as super easy access to I-35 to head south towards Austin and North towards Temple/Waco.  
This home features 4 sides brick, fireplace, small storage building and large back yard that backs up to acreage for some privacy as well.  The home has tile throughout the living and kitchen area and carpet in the bedrooms. Both the primary bath and hall bath have double sinks!
This home offers the rare opportunity to own in this small neighborhood.  This would make an excellent family home or a first home for someone beginning their home ownership.
